WEBVTT

02:38.575 --> 02:40.577
EPISODE 2 LOCKSMITH

02:47.375 --> 02:48.293
TWO PEOPLE AGAINST ONE

02:48.376 --> 02:49.294
WHAT IF I MAKE THEM MAD?

02:49.377 --> 02:50.211
THEY'RE MAKING FUN OF ME

02:50.295 --> 02:51.713
A WASTE OF TIME

03:16.863 --> 03:19.407
I CAN'T GET HERE UNLESS I USE THAT CROSSWALK OVER THERE

03:30.835 --> 03:35.757
SWIFT

03:36.966 --> 03:39.385
BLURRY

03:45.975 --> 03:50.146
HURRY

05:37.128 --> 05:39.172
AFTER ALL THIS TIME

05:47.597 --> 05:50.767
THE HURDLE TO ADDRESSING HIM
I WANTED TO KNOW HIS LAST NAME

06:37.021 --> 06:40.441
WE'RE PRETTY CLOSE

07:04.173 --> 07:05.174
SPARKLE SPARKLE SPARKLE SPARKLE

07:06.175 --> 07:07.176
BANG

07:23.693 --> 07:25.695
MEITEN COMMUNITY CENTER

08:39.310 --> 08:41.312
WELL DONE, MOM

09:32.738 --> 09:39.412
FLUSTER

09:39.495 --> 09:43.666
NATURAL SPARKLING LEMON WATER
REFRESHING AND DELICIOUS APPLE JUICE

09:43.749 --> 09:45.668
SHAKE SHAKE
I FEEL BAD

09:52.008 --> 09:59.015
COCOA, SWEET RED BEAN SOUP,
AMAZAKE CORN POTAGE

10:33.174 --> 10:34.759
STRETCH

10:59.950 --> 11:01.410
SHE DOESN'T GET CALLED BY HER FIRST NAME MUCH TO BEGIN WITH

12:32.251 --> 12:33.085
SQUISH

12:40.426 --> 12:41.969
INCOMING CALL

15:01.942 --> 15:04.987
HE DOES THIS IF I DON'T KEEP AN EYE ON HIM

15:05.070 --> 15:08.365
BA-DUMP, BA-DUMP

16:01.126 --> 16:03.545
SCHOOL NURSE'S OFFICE

16:13.263 --> 16:15.265
RELIEVED

17:01.061 --> 17:03.230
BRISKLY

17:43.729 --> 17:45.147
BAM

18:07.628 --> 18:09.671
I KIND OF LIKE IT

18:14.009 --> 18:15.928
SPACE FOR ONE PERSON

18:24.561 --> 18:27.606
STEPPING BACK

18:48.085 --> 18:54.758
HUFF, HUFF

18:55.008 --> 18:56.760
FOGGY

19:14.111 --> 19:19.575
THEY TEND TO TALK A LITTLE MORE WHEN
THEY ARE ABOUT TO SAY GOODBYE

19:32.421 --> 19:35.340
BECAUSE I'M ONLY A HIGH SCHOOL STUDENT

19:35.424 --> 19:38.302
ONE THOUSAND YEN

19:38.385 --> 19:41.555
SHOP MANAGER

21:13.105 --> 21:15.107
GRADE 1 CLASS 6

21:33.875 --> 21:36.336
THAT WAY, IT'LL ALSO BE EASIER FOR MIKI TO CONTACT US

21:36.628 --> 21:37.713
THAT'S TRUE
